{"image_id": "MKC_2012_page_29", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "McCormick & Company    2012 Annual Report    page 25", "bbox": [876.2, 1582.7, 1150.0, 1601.9]}, {"text": "ITEM 5. MARKET FOR REGISTRANT’S COMMON EQUITY, RELATED STOCKHOLDER MATTERS AND ISSUER PURCHASES OF", "bbox": [125.0, 184.2, 1093.4, 207.1]}, {"text": "EQUITY SECURITIES", "bbox": [125.0, 207.1, 285.6, 230.0]}, {"text": "We have disclosed in note 16 of the ﬁnancial statements the information relating to the market price and dividends paid on our classes of common", "bbox": [125.0, 242.9, 1150.5, 265.4]}, {"text": "stock. The market price of our common stock at the close of business on December 31, 2012 was $63.22 per share for the Common Stock and", "bbox": [125.0, 265.8, 1127.7, 288.3]}, {"text": "$63.53 per share for the Common Stock Non-Voting.", "bbox": [125.0, 288.7, 490.0, 311.2]}, {"text": "Our Common Stock and Common Stock Non-Voting are listed and traded on the New York Stock Exchange (“NYSE”). The approximate number of", "bbox": [125.0, 334.5, 1137.1, 357.1]}, {"text": "holders of our common stock based on record ownership as of December 31, 2012 was as follows:", "bbox": [125.0, 357.4, 808.5, 380.0]}, {"text": "Title of Class", "bbox": [300.0, 421.9, 381.6, 442.0]}, {"text": "Approximate Number", "bbox": [830.2, 401.1, 967.2, 421.2]}, {"text": "of Record Holders", "bbox": [841.1, 421.9, 952.6, 442.0]}, {"text": "Common Stock, no par value", "bbox": [300.0, 451.6, 477.5, 471.7]}, {"text": "2,100", "bbox": [883.6, 451.6, 916.7, 471.7]}, {"text": "Common Stock Non-Voting, no par value", "bbox": [300.0, 472.5, 551.6, 492.5]}, {"text": "10,200", "bbox": [874.6, 472.5, 916.7, 492.5]}, {"text": "The following table summarizes our purchases of Common Stock (CS) and Common Stock Non-Voting (CSNV) during the fourth quarter of 2012:", "bbox": [125.0, 529.8, 1122.1, 552.4]}, {"text": "ISSUER PURCHASES OF EQUITY SECURITIES", "bbox": [480.2, 573.6, 794.8, 596.2]}, {"text": "Period", "bbo